<div class="container" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; color: #333;">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-10 offset-md-1">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="card mb-5 border-0 shadow-lg" style="border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden;">
        <div class="card-body p-0">
          <div style="position: relative;">
            <img src="/images/about-hero.jpg" alt="Happy pets collage" class="img-fluid w-100" style="height: 400px; object-fit: cover;" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450778869180-41d0601e046e?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80'">
            <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);"></div>
            <div style="position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); text-align: center; width: 100%;">
              <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-white" style="text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">Our Passion for Pets</h1>
              <p class="lead text-white" style="font-size: 1.5rem; text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">Creating happy tails since <%= new Date().getFullYear() - 2 %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission Section -->
      <div class="card mb-5 border-0 shadow-sm" style="border-radius: 15px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);">
        <div class="card-body p-5">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
              <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4" style="color: #2c3e50;">Our Mission</h2>
              <p class="lead" style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7;">
                At PetAdopt, we're dedicated to transforming the pet adoption experience by connecting loving homes with animals in need, while providing comprehensive resources for pet care, products, and veterinary services.
              </p>
              <p style="line-height: 1.7;">
                We believe every pet deserves a forever home filled with love, and every owner deserves access to the best care and products for their furry family members.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <img src="/images/mission-pets.jpg" alt="Diverse pets together" class="img-fluid rounded shadow" style="border: 5px solid white;" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583511655826-05700442b31b?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=634&q=80'">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What We Do Section -->
      <div class="card mb-5 border-0 shadow-sm" style="border-radius: 15px;">
        <div class="card-body p-5">
          <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-5" style="color: #2c3e50;">What We Offer</h2>
          
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
              <div class="text-center p-4 h-100" style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; transition: all 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-5px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform=''; this.style.boxShadow='none'">
                <div class="mb-3" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background-color: #e3f2fd; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                  <i class="fas fa-paw fa-2x" style="color: #1976d2;"></i>
                </div>
                <h4 style="color: #1976d2;">Adoption</h4>
                <p>Connecting loving homes with pets in need through our network of trusted shelters and rescues.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
              <div class="text-center p-4 h-100" style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; transition: all 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-5px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform=''; this.style.boxShadow='none'">
                <div class="mb-3" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background-color: #e8f5e9; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                  <i class="fas fa-shopping-bag fa-2x" style="color: #388e3c;"></i>
                </div>
                <h4 style="color: #388e3c;">Products</h4>
                <p>Curated marketplace of high-quality pet supplies from trusted vendors and small businesses.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
              <div class="text-center p-4 h-100" style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; transition: all 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-5px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform=''; this.style.boxShadow='none'">
                <div class="mb-3" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background-color: #fff3e0; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                  <i class="fas fa-stethoscope fa-2x" style="color: #e65100;"></i>
                </div>
                <h4 style="color: #e65100;">Care</h4>
                <p>Easy access to veterinary services, grooming, and pet care professionals in your area.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Story Section -->
      <div class="card mb-5 border-0 shadow-sm" style="border-radius: 15px; background-color: #2c3e50;">
        <div class="card-body p-5 text-white">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
              <img src="/images/founders.jpg" alt="PetAdopt founders with pets" class="img-fluid rounded shadow" style="border: 5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568640347023-a616a30bc3bd?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=634&q=80'">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
              <p style="line-height: 1.7;">
                PetAdopt was founded in <%= new Date().getFullYear() - 2 %> by a team of animal lovers who saw the challenges in the pet adoption process. What began as a simple idea to make adoption easier has grown into a comprehensive platform serving thousands of pets and owners nationwide.
              </p>
              <p style="line-height: 1.7;">
                Today, we're proud to have facilitated over 10,000 successful adoptions and partnered with hundreds of shelters and pet care professionals to create a better world for our furry friends.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Values Section -->
