                    <i class="fas fa-heart fa-lg" style="color: #d32f2f;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="color: #d32f2f;">Compassion First</h4>
                  <p>Every decision we make is guided by our love for animals and commitment to their wellbeing.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="me-4" style="min-width: 60px;">
                  <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: #e8f5e9; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart fa-lg" style="color: #388e3c;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="color: #388e3c;">Community Focus</h4>
                  <p>We build bridges between shelters, pet owners, and care providers to create a supportive network.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="me-4" style="min-width: 60px;">
                  <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: #fff3e0; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <i class="fas fa-award fa-lg" style="color: #e65100;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="color: #e65100;">Excellence</h4>
                  <p>We maintain the highest standards for all pets, products, and services on our platform.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <div class="me-4" style="min-width: 60px;">
                  <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: #f3e5f5; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb fa-lg" style="color: #7b1fa2;"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="color: #7b1fa2;">Innovation</h4>
                  <p>We continuously improve our platform to better serve pets and their humans.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Impact Stats -->
      <div class="card mb-5 border-0 shadow-sm" style="border-radius: 15px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a148c 0%, #7b1fa2 100%);">
        <div class="card-body p-5 text-white">
          <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-5">Our Impact</h2>
          
          <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
              <div class="display-4 fw-bold mb-2" style="color: #ffeb3b;">10,000+</div>
              <div>Pets Adopted</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
              <div class="display-4 fw-bold mb-2" style="color: #4caf50;">200+</div>
              <div>Shelter Partners</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
              <div class="display-4 fw-bold mb-2" style="color: #03a9f4;">5,000+</div>
              <div>Happy Families</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
              <div class="display-4 fw-bold mb-2" style="color: #ff9800;">50+</div>
              <div>Cities Served</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm" style="border-radius: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
        <div class="card-body p-5 text-center">
          <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4" style="color: #2c3e50;">Join Our Community</h2>
          <p class="lead mb-5" style="max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
            Whether you're looking to adopt, volunteer, or support our mission, there's a place for you in the PetAdopt family.
          </p>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="/pets" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 py-3" style="border-radius: 12px; min-width: 200px; font-weight: 600;">Find a Pet</a>
